70'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_baltimore4.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=6205'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_montpelier14.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=14581'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_baltimore5.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>07 Dec 1944</div><a href='/image.php?image_id=2343'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis54.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=2344'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis55.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=2345'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis56.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=2346'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis57.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>09 Dec 1944</div><a href='/image.php?image_id=2341'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis52.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=2342'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis53.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>03 Jul 1945</div><a href='/image.php?image_id=7013'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_pensacola7.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>10 Jul 1945</div><a href='/image.php?image_id=1455'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis22.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=1456'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis23.jpg' style='width: 50px; margin-right: 3px;' /></a><br /><a href='/image.php?image_id=1457'><img src='/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_indianapolis24.jpg' st